tate: none; scale: none; transform: translate(0%, 19.3902%) translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);"></div><!-- Gradient Overlay --><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/40 to-black/80 z-10"></div><!-- Content --><div class="relative z-20 container mx-auto px-6 text-center mt-16"><p class="text-luxury-gold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm md:text-base font-semibold mb-4" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"> A symphony of elegance </p><h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-serif text-white font-medium mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-xl" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"> Discover the<br>Art of Luxury </h1><p class="text-gray-200 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light drop-shadow-md" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"> Immerse yourself in unparalleled comfort and refined sophistication at Lumina. Your exclusive sanctuary awaits. </p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"><a href="http://localhost:5173/#discover" class="bg-luxury-gold hover:bg-luxury-gold-hover text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-sm font-medium tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300 min-w-[200px]"> Discover More </a><a href="http://localhost:5173/#book" class="bg-transparent border border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-sm font-medium tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300 min-w-[200px]"> Reserve Your Stay </a></div></div><!-- Scroll Down Indicator --><div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-20 flex flex-col items-center animate-bounce"><span class="text-white/70 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-medium">Scroll</span><div class="w-[1px] h-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-luxury-gold to-transparent"></div></div></section><section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-luxury-dark overflow-hidden"><div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12"><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 lg:gap-24"><!-- Image Area --><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"><div class="relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-square lg:aspect-[3/4]"><img src="./gallery5_files/photo-1582719508461-905c673771fd" alt="Luxury Hotel Interior" class="object-cover w-full h-full transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"></div><!-- Decorative element --><div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-2/3 aspect-square bg-slate-100 dark:bg-luxury-surface -z-10 rounded-sm"></div><div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-luxury-gold -z-10"></div></div><!-- Text Area --><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2"><p class="text-luxury-gold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-4" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"><span class="w-12 h-px bg-luxury-gold inline-block"></span> Heritage &amp; Modernity </p><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium mb-8 leading-tight" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"> A sanctuary of calm <br> in the heart of the city. </h2><p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"> Since 1985, Lumina has been a symbol of uncompromising luxury and impeccable service. We've crafted an environment where timeless elegance meets modern sophistication. </p><p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate3d(0px, 0.0007px, 0px);"> Every room, every meal, and every moment is designed to transform an ordinary stay into an extraordinary experience. Drift away in our award-winning spa or dine under the stars. </p><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0.9895; transform: translate3d(0px, 0.3146px, 0px);"><div><p class="text-4xl font-serif text-luxury-gold mb-2">5<span class="text-2xl">★</span></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Luxury Rating</p></div><div><p class="text-4xl font-serif text-luxury-gold mb-2">320</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Premium Suites</p></div></div><a href="http://localhost:5173/#history" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 group text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium hover:text-luxury-gold transition-colors" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0.8944; transform: translate3d(0px, 3.1668px, 0px);"><span class="pb-1 border-b border-transparent group-hover:border-luxury-gold transition-colors">Read Our Story</span><svg class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section id="services" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#080d1e] overflow-hidden"><div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12"><!-- Section Header --><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 md:mb-24"><p class="text-luxury-gold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Exceptional Offerings</p><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium mb-6"> Tailored to your desires </h2><div class="h-px w-24 bg-luxury-gold mx-auto"></div></div><!-- Services Cards --><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12"><div class="group bg-white dark:bg-luxury-surface border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 rounded-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 50px);"><div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div><img src="./gallery5_files/photo-1514933651103-005eec06c04b" alt="Culinary Experiences" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div><div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow"><h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-luxury-gold transition-colors">Culinary Experiences</h3><p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">Savor exquisite dishes prepared by our Michelin-starred chefs, blending local ingredients with global techniques in a stunning panoramic setting.</p><a href="http://localhost:5173/#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-luxury-gold font-medium group/link uppercase text-sm tracking-widest mt-auto">View Menu <svg class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover/link:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class="group bg-white dark:bg-luxury-surface border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 rounded-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 50px);"><div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div><img src="./gallery5_files/photo-1611892440504-42a792e24d32" alt="Rooms &amp; Suites" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div><div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow"><h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-luxury-gold transition-colors">Rooms &amp; Suites</h3><p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">Retreat to your private haven. Unwind in opulently designed suites offering breathtaking views, bespoke furnishings, and intuitive smart-room technology.</p><a href="http://localhost:5173/#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-luxury-gold font-medium group/link uppercase text-sm tracking-widest mt-auto">Explore Rooms <svg class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover/link:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class="group bg-white dark:bg-luxury-surface border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 rounded-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 50px);"><div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div><img src="./gallery5_files/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874" alt="Wellness &amp; Spa" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div><div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow"><h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-luxury-gold transition-colors">Wellness &amp; Spa</h3><p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">Rejuvenate mind, body, and soul in our holistic wellness center. Indulge in bespoke treatments, thermal baths, and personalized yoga sessions.</p><a href="http://localhost:5173/#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-luxury-gold font-medium group/link uppercase text-sm tracking-widest mt-auto">Discover Spa <svg class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover/link:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section data-v-7846a2bc="" id="gallery" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-luxury-dark"><div data-v-7846a2bc="" class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12"><!-- Section Header --><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8" data-v-7846a2bc=""><div class="max-w-xl" data-v-7846a2bc=""><p class="text-luxury-gold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-4" data-v-7846a2bc="">Aesthetics &amp; Design</p><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium" data-v-7846a2bc=""> Visual Journey </h2></div><a href="http://localhost:5173/#" class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white border-b border-luxury-gold pb-1 hover:text-luxury-gold transition-colors uppercase text-sm tracking-widest font-medium" data-v-7846a2bc=""> View Full Gallery </a></div><!-- Masonry Grid --><div data-v-7846a2bc="" class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 auto-rows-[200px]"><div data-v-7846a2bc="" class="col-span-2 row-span-2 relative group overflow-hidden cursor-pointer rounded-sm bg-slate-100 dark:bg-luxury-surface" style="translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"><img data-v-7846a2bc="" src="./gallery5_files/photo-1578683010236-d716f9a3f461" alt="Gallery entry" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"><div data-v-7846a2bc="" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex i