597fc7="" class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full px-4" style="display: none;"><p data-v-69597fc7="" class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-relaxed mb-8 italic"> "A true sanctuary in the bustling city. The spa treatments reset my entirely, and the concierge preemptively knew exactly what I needed." </p><div data-v-69597fc7=""><p data-v-69597fc7="" class="text-luxury-gold font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Sarah J.</p><p data-v-69597fc7="" class="text-slate-500 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Business Executive</p></div></div></div></div><div data-v-69597fc7="" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-12"><button data-v-69597fc7="" class="p-3 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:bg-luxury-gold hover:border-luxury-gold text-slate-700 dark:text-white transition-colors group"><svg data-v-69597fc7="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 group-hover:text-white lucide-chevron-left-icon lucide-chevron-left w-5 h-5 group-hover:text-white" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-v-69597fc7="" class="flex gap-2 mx-4"><button data-v-69597fc7="" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-luxury-gold w-6" aria-label="Go to testimonial"></button><button data-v-69597fc7="" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-slate-300 dark:bg-white/20" aria-label="Go to testimonial"></button><button data-v-69597fc7="" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-slate-300 dark:bg-white/20" aria-label="Go to testimonial"></button></div><button data-v-69597fc7="" class="p-3 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:bg-luxury-gold hover:border-luxury-gold text-slate-700 dark:text-white transition-colors group"><svg 